data_table.description: Insulin-like Growth Factor 1 (IGF-1) and Insulin-like Growth Factor Binding Protein 3 (IGFBP-3), Generation 3 Cohort Exam 1

variable.name: igf1
variable.comment: Cases which measured below the lowest detectable assay limit of 9.4 ng/ml were set to 9.00 ng/ml (n=10)

variable.name: igfbp3
variable.comment: Cases which measured below the lowest detectable assay limit of 75.99 ng/ml were set to 75.00 ng/ml (n=3). Cases above measurable limit of 5000 ng/ml were set to 5001 ng/ml (n=319). The user should determine how to handle these cases.
